net.smartcosmos.model.context

Interface IAccount

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDomainResource<IAccount>, IMoniker, INamedObject<IAccount>, IUrnNamespace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Account

    public interface IAccount
extends IDomainResource<IAccount>, INamedObject<IAccount>
    Collection of foundational attributes that define a platform subscription. Each IAccount will have a unique public-private key generated at creation time. The private key is securely managed by the platform and is inaccessible to all. The public key is accessible to account administrators, and may be used to verify digitally signed data downloaded from platform to confirm it hasn't been tampered with after download.
